Lemma tauVEF_alt1 v w: `v,w IN dart_of_fan (V,E)
	==> let f = face (hypermap_of_fan (V,E)) (v,w) in
		tauVEF (V,E,f) = sol (vec 0) (dart_leads_into (vec 0) V E v w)
		  + (&2 - &(CARD f)) * sol0
		  - sol0 / pi * sum f (\x. azim_dart (V,E) x * (lmfun (h_dart x) - &1))`.
